column5: While out for a drive an hour ago, I couldn't believe what I saw. Is this what Spiel does in his spare time?
That boxcar is probably full of custom made fish'n poles
Hey that looks like the sig on my fishin pole! Joe
....Oh sure, have a good laugh at my expense. Wait a minute usually everyone is laughing at my expense, it takes the heat of TJ.
Naa, we still laugh at him too!
So that what you do at the new Yankee work shop
